00:17:00.790 --> 00:17:03.430
The probe that we're
using in this nano MRI

00:17:03.430 --> 00:17:04.995
is nanometer sized.

00:17:04.995 --> 00:17:07.119
So this gives us the ability
to look at things that

00:17:07.119 --> 00:17:08.750
