00:37:04.650 --> 00:37:06.436
All right, let's just
do 10 more seconds.

00:37:22.980 --> 00:37:30.310
We're varying it up
in terms of the plots.

00:37:30.310 --> 00:37:40.970
So maybe someone want to say
what the right answer is here?

00:37:40.970 --> 00:37:41.470
Yeah?

